{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_02_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 ダンス以外の趣味を",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私、お菓子作りをします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to try my hand at making desserts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8666666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.166666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それが怜の新しい趣味なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that your new hobby?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.166666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "まだ決めてませんが、みんなに聞いたら\nお菓子が好きな子がとても多くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven’t decided‚\nbut many of our members likes to eat sweets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.933333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、私が美味しいのを作れたら\nみんなにも喜んでもらえると思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll make delicious desserts that\nmake the other girls happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "女の子っぽくていいとは思うけど……\n俺が呼ばれたってことは、一緒に作るのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess it’s a pretty nice hobby…\nBut why did you call me? Do you need an assistant?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.366666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、試食をお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I need a taster.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それだったら\n他の子達に食べてもらえばいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Won’t one of the other girls\nbe a better choice for that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.433333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "ダメ。出来の悪いモノをみんなに食べてほしくないから\n……練習して、完璧になったらみんなにあげます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope. I can’t make them eat my failed attempts.\nI’ll only show it to them once I’ve gotten everything down perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺は練習台か……。負けず嫌いの怜らしいけど\n趣味なんだから、そんなに気負わなくても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you need a guinea pig… I know you’re a perfectionist‚\nbut do you really need to go this far? It’s just a hobby.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.333333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "一年以内に、レシピ本を出して\n全てのレシピ本を過去のモノにする意気込みです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m coming in with the mentality of publishing\nmy own recipe book in a year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "おいおい……\nそもそも趣味じゃなくて仕事になってるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa…\nAt that point‚ it stops being a hobby and starts being a job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだから、芸能活動にも役立つ趣味の方が\nいいじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’m going to pick up a hobby‚\nI might as well pick one that could be of use to my career.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんも雑誌の一人キャンプ特集に\n載ってたじゃないですか。あんな感じで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ for example‚\nhas had her own featured magazine article on solo camping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もともと趣味だったのが仕事になるのは分かる\nでも、怜のは順番が逆だろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I could understand blending a hobby that you already have into your work.\nBut it’s the opposite here‚ isn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "でも何か目標がないと\n張り合いがないじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no point in doing something\nwithout setting a goal for myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "何かのスイッチが入っちゃったか……\nまぁいい。何を作るんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like you’re got your mind set.\nFine. What are you planning on making?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "はい、マカロンです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to try my hand at macarons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "分かった\nじゃあ、ネットで簡単な作り方を検索しようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay then.\nLet’s look for recipes online.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、作り方は、昨日調べました\nフランスの有名シェフのレシピが公開されていたので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve already looked up the recipe.\nIt’s from a famous French chef.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ぶ厚い資料だな……え？　フランス語……なのか？\nこれ全部読んだのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ that’s a lot of material… Huh? Is this… in French?\nDid you read all of it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 105.06666666666666
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1900.0000000000057,
          "startTime": 106.96666666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3900.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 108.96666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "はい。読破しました\n検索サイトを使いながらですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ cover to cover.\nIn conjunction with a search engine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "日本語のレシピならいくらでもあるのに……\n俺にはよく分からないけど、難しそうだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I would have just looked for recipes in Japanese…\nI don’t know any French‚ but it looks hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "やるからには、最高のレシピで作りたいと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I’m going to do it‚ I might as well find the best recipe possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.23333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "初心者なんだから、簡単なレシピから始めた方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I would go with a simple recipe to start out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "いいですから、{user}さんは\n出来上がるまで大人しく待ってて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never mind that.\n{user}-san‚ you just take a seat while I get to work.",
